ğŸ”Œ Backend API Requirement
The frontend expects a backend endpoint:
POST /analyze
Content-Type: application/json
Request Body
{
  "code": "string",
  "language": "auto | javascript | python | java | cpp"
}
Example Response
{
  "type": "ai",
  "confidence": 82,
  "reasons": [
    "Highly regular formatting",
    "Low comment density"
  ],
  "model": "Heuristic + OpenAI"
}
________________________________________
âš ï¸ Common Setup Note (Vite)
If you see this warning in the terminal:
Malformed URI sequence in request URL: /%PUBLIC_URL%/favicon.ico
It means the favicon path is using Create React App syntax, which is not supported by Vite.
âœ… Fix
Open index.html and replace:
<link rel="icon" href="%PUBLIC_URL%/favicon.ico" />
with:
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
Then restart the dev server:
npm run dev
